data.title: Watch ATXN Live
data.meta_description: ATXN1: Same feed as programming on the flagship ATXN TV channel.  Programming includes Council meetings, public meetings, CityView and other original programming. ATXN2: This web only channel includes meetings when more than one meeting is taking place at City Hall as well as original programming. ATXN3: Este canal transmite nuestra programación y contenido en español.
data.text:
ATXN1: Same feed as programming on the flagship ATXN TV channel. Programming includes Council meetings, public meetings, CityView and other original programming.

ATXN2: This web only channel includes meetings when more than one meeting is taking place at City Hall as well as original programming.

ATXN3: Este canal transmite nuestra programación y contenido en español.
